node.text:
Hi! MY FIRST EVER IGTV ! My friends and I decided to visit LA and we went out the day before so we decided to stay inside and this is what our night consisted of... HAHA! They had been begging to play hide and seek that whole week and I was NOT feeling it 😭 If you’d like more videos like this, vote on the poll on my Instagram story or comment below! 
Subscribe to Youtube.com/MsAaliyahJay for more videos + vlogs

Follow @Jay_lindo + @iamalexpatrick 
Filmed by @alrdysuccessful

node.title: A NIGHT INSIDE WITH MY FRIENDS
